message: Hello Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs. After careful consideration, I believe we can come to an agreement that benefits both of us. I am offering this exceptional product to you for $18000. This price reflects not only the value of the product but also the expertise and support we provide to ensure its successful integration into your operations.

However, to maintain a fair balance, I propose a price of $16500 for the product. This still allows us to cover our costs and provides some room for negotiation while ensuring you receive a high-quality product.
